353
00:19:18,490 --> 00:19:19,491
Yes.

354
00:19:20,492 --> 00:19:22,911
(indistinct radio chatter)

355
00:19:23,996 --> 00:19:25,539
INSPECTION, PLEASE COOPERATE

356
00:19:25,622 --> 00:19:27,624
(tense music)

357
00:19:30,169 --> 00:19:31,170
